{
  "stem": "26142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we are trying to go back to our birthplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That the local people shouldn't hinder us, that they should help us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was pleading with him, with this priest, to give us a letter, that kind of a letter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said he would do it but he noticed that she was wearing a diamond ring.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he, for that-- for that thing, he wanted that she should give him that diamond ring.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we talked it over among ourselves and we decided this isn't-- this isn't worthwhile to invest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know, this was her-- her wedding-- wedding, the ring that she got, diamond.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That she was wearing it on her hand, that was stupid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's besides the point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that's what it was, she was still wearing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened was that we decided that this is too high a price to pay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That if we would give him 100 Hungarian pengos-- this was Hungarian money-- if he would write us such a recommendation letter to-- to-- to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he finally-- he finally decided to do that and he gave us a letter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, we told him that the [NON-ENGLISH], this was the Ukrainian national movement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we know it and the Carpathian-- it wasn't all-- all-- all true that we are so friendly with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were plenty afraid of him but we had no other way of-- of obtaining this letter from him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We finally obtained that letter from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, and here I come to the-- one day, the three brothers, three and I and Moshe, decided to go out to the farmers and try to buy some food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe we can buy either flour or-- or bread or-- or cheese, cottage cheese, milk, something.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
